### **4.2 Value Creation Calculation**

```
Value Theory Framework:
â”œâ”€â”€ Time Saved: Hours Ã— Hourly Value Rate
â”œâ”€â”€ Bad Experience Avoided: Frequency Ã— Average Loss
â”œâ”€â”€ Discovery Value: New Experiences Ã— Experience Value
â”œâ”€â”€ Social Value: Sharing/Recommendations Ã— Network Effect
â””â”€â”€ Restaurant Value: Customer Acquisition Ã— LTV Improvement
