#### **Example Value Calculation:**
```
Consumer Value Per Year:
â”œâ”€â”€ Time saved researching: 20 hours Ã— $25/hour = $500
â”œâ”€â”€ Bad experiences avoided: 5 Ã— $50 = $250
â”œâ”€â”€ Discovery of hidden gems: 12 Ã— $20 value = $240
â”œâ”€â”€ Social sharing value: $50
â””â”€â”€ Total Annual Value = $1,040

